          "activation_name": "Disgorge Soul",
          "effect": "The *soulfeeding mask* disgorges the devoured soul. You\u2019re no longer quickened from Devour Soul, and the soulfeeding mask casts *duplicate foe* (DC 36 Fortitude save) to your specifications, targeting the creature whose soul had been devoured. You must Sustain this effect, unless the target creature was slain by Devour Soul, in which case duplicate foe functions as if the creature had failed its save, and the *soulfeeding mask* Sustains this spell automatically.",
          "links": [
